this_title: The House at the End of the Road
introduction: Four students majoring in art leave the civilization for a couple of days to be able to dedicate some time to their current art projects. They've rented a remote house where the nearest neighbour is miles away and nothing but woods surround them, but just as they start getting settled in, strange things start to occur. Something's been waiting for them and now there's only one rule; trust no one... ESPECIALLY not yourself!
